fields.label: Possible Provider Names
fields.name: possible_provider_names
fields.instructions: Please add each possible name that the FCC database or Bundle Dealers API might have for this provider. For example, Hughesnet might be "Hughesnet" or "Hughsnet". Case and spacing matter.

fields.label: Buyer
fields.name: buyer
fields.instructions: Note that you must save this Provider with the list of Possible Names before any Buyers will populate the dropdown. Once Buyers are populating the dropdown, you must save the Provider again in order for the Buyer selection to save.

sub_fields.instructions: Show asterisk above the price on the zip search results
